<pre class='note'>Description:
------------
Tested on PHP 7  on 32 bits with ASAN and using USE_ZEND_ALLOC=0.

user@Xenial32-2:~/crashes/gd$ USE_ZEND_ALLOC=0 gdb -q --args /home/user/php-7.0/sapi/cli/php -n phuzz4.php

